text:
The only time we crossed each other on the campus was - I came out after seeing the end sem paper of Power Electronics and you were going inside. You were like yeh banda kafi khush lag raha hai and you asked kafi jyada no aye hai kya. I didnâ€™t answer anything. Uss waqat mai jyada baat karne ke moond mai tha nahi. Barely passed that course. I donâ€™t know how.

All the Best man. Good Luck for your bucket list.
author: Aryan  Choudhary

text: Hey guys i want to wish you all a merry christmas. Discord is full of copypasted christmas messages, that people don't even read and just forward to other servers. I don't like that. I like to write what i deeply wish and what comes from my heart. Our friendships, from the most deep ones to the most virtual ones are very important and will never be represented by a simple message copied from elsewhere. This being said I would like to thank all of you. You are the best hockey team i've ever played with.
author: Aryan  Choudhary

text:
Hum toh ESC101A ke piazza par kafi bakchodiya (aka spam) karte the. Fir ek din messenger par baate start ki thi. Uss din ghante bhar baate karte gaye the. That how our friendship started. Fir aye din saat mai CSE OE reject hone par thoda roh lete the. FB par toh spam bahut hi kiya hai.
Teri chocolates due hai.
Good Bye. All the Best bhai.

text:
Hello Nikita ğŸ”«,
Tune 1000 bar kaha tha Memoirs likh de. I was like likh hi denge. Bahut time hai. Now here Iâ€™m creating a petition on change.org for a deadline extension XD. Mere rr sunne ke liye Thank you. Batti club mai hi mile the ya TA lab mai yaad nahi. Humare section aye din same hote the. Pata nahi doaa office walo ka kaisa random number generator tha. Batti200 ki toh maine ek hi mini quiz di thi iirc. TA ki lab mai toh full fraud mara tha. 3 ghanto ki lab mai unwritten rule tha roj 1.5 ghante se jyada kaam nahi karna. Baki time poori lab mai bakchodi karni. Bajarbatti ki lab mai poora kaam mere lab partners hi karte the. Last mai meri reading barabar aa jati thi fir bhi. Waha bhi kafi bakchodiya ki thi. Last tak toh TAs ko bhi pata chal hi gaya tha yeh kuch kaam nahi karta kyoki toh tune hi TA ko bol diya tha isko kuch nahi aata. ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚
Mai hamesha sarcastic way mai ulta bolta tha. Tuje kabhi samaj nahi aata tha. Aise bahut maje liye hai tere. ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚
At last toh yahi bolunga maje karna.
author: Aryan  Choudhary

text:
Bhai tu yaaro ka yaar hai. 
Same coaching se the. Coaching mai ek baar ladai bhi kar li thi. Fir bhi jab hum orientation mile muje bilkul yaad nahi tha tu kaun hai. Muje toh uss waqat aisa tha ki tujse pehli baar mil raha hu.
Yeh kissa toh tum dono mai se koi kabhi nahi bhulne wala. ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ Jab bhi hum dono kisi aur se milenge tu yeh usko batae bina nahi rehne wala. As always I will be like bhai ab kya karu mai. 

Uncle Ji ke ghar firse Diwali par jarur chalenge.
Mere saare bhaiyo se alag alag jagah mila tha. Jab tu pehli baar humare room par aya tha toh. Literally tuje toh haar 2 min mai shock mil raha tha. You were like - Yeh bhi tera bhai hai? Yeh bhi tera bhai hai? ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚

Agar kisi ka BDay aata tha aur tere paas agar uski photo nahi hoti thi. Toh tu sabse pehle uski photo ka jugad karta tha. Uske baad uss photo ko upload karke BDay wish karta tha.

Finally kafi mehnate insaan hai tu. Thoda dara hua bhi rehta hai. Aage apna kya hoga. 
Muje jitna yaad hai backlog toh teri sirf ek course mai hi ayi thi. Vo course mai teesari baar kar raha hu. Abhi bhi pata nahi iss baar bhi niklega ya nahi. Padhta tu regular tha. Saat mai shayad fail ho sakte hai vo daar thoda constant tha tera. 
Tere no/cpi dekh kar tere ghar walo ko lagta hoga. Bilkul padhta likhta nahi hai. Par tuje pata hai aur muje bhi pata hai mehnat mai tune kahi koi kami nahi rakhi hai. Ab relative grading mai no nahi aate toh vo toh apne haat mai nahi. 

Ek baar tu EE250A ki quiz se pehle muje NCL mai mila tha. Maine kuch bhi padh nahi rakha tha. Bode plot tune muje itna aache se samjhaya tha ki mai aaj tak nahi bhula hu. Par tu khud bhul gaya tha. Mid sem mai ussi NCL mai muje tuje samjhana pada tha. ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚

TA ka project poora kaise uski poore grp mai sabse jyada chinta tuje thi. Uss sem tu grp mai kisi se bhi milta toh TA project ka poochta tha. Kisi koi idea nahi hota tha kya chal raha hai. Par haar koi kisi aur ka naam leh kar bol deta tha. Vo toh kar hi raha hoga. Tu chill maar ho jayaga. Finally katam ho toh gaya tha. ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚

Finally itna bata raha hu ki tu jitni mehnat karta hai usse ek bahut aachi jagah pauch jayaga. Abhi tuje kafi daar lag raha hoga aage apna kya hoga. But thoda chill maar. Badiya hi hoga. All the Best.
author: Aryan  Choudhary

text:
Bhai sabse pehle hum CHM101A lab mai hi mile the. TA muje handwriting theek karne ko bol raha tha. Iâ€™m ab toh school se bahar nikal. Jo aaj tak theek nahi karwa paya vo tum karwa doge. Its unwritten rule ki CHM101A pass karna hai toh test tube todna jaruri hai. Toh yeh kaam bhi humne aache se kar hi liya tha. Bhai bahut maje kiye the lab mai. These days tere paas itna free time kaise hai. FB/IIM par itna active. 
Mai toh tere yaha â€œ... am here.â€ spam karwane ke liye ready tha. Ab log hi nahi chatte toh mai kya karu. 
Bhai kuch bhi ho jaye toh haste haste nikal dega. Kafi talent hai bahut aage jayaga. All the Best bhai.
author: Aryan  Choudhary

text:
Yo bro,
Muje most logo ka yaad hai sabse pehle kaha mile the. But tumhara bilkul yaad nahi. Ig kisi hall event mai mile honge jaha maine eventually fraud maar liya hoga. The first thing we did together was setting problems for FPC. Hum dono late lunch/dinner karne mess mai aate the. Mostly baate mess ya wing mai hi karte the. Baad mai toh as pclub secy kafi kaam kar liye the. Thank you for being with me in the summers. Kafi maje aye the un summers mai. Tumhari debugging skills kafi weak thi. Hamesha kuch na kuch bug reh jata tha. Ngl 1-2 baar muje gussa bhi aya tha bhai yeh kyo nahi debug ho raha. 
Good Luck for the future.
author: Aryan  Choudhary

text:
First year mai toh - Yeh Aryan ko kuch nahi bolega. Baadme isko mth ke doubts bhi poochne hai. Ha tu jo yeh bataâ€¦ 
Ek baar raat ko Yogi tere thode maje leh raha tha tu ekdum se utha kar humare room mai. Usse ladne aa gaya tha. Uske baad vo jab bhi tere thode maje leta tha toh pehle aas paas dekhta tha fir bahut dhire se bolta tha. Mai aur Uncle ji uske maje lete the. Ab aawaj nahi niklegi uski. 
Fir 2nd year mai roll aaye din mangwate rehte the. 
Antaragni mai hum sab Ball room mai chale gaye the. Uske baad poori wing walo ke jo humne maje liye the vo tohâ€¦ Govind ke to ek baar maje liye the SIS guard ban kar vo toh..,

DR 1 bhi finally ban gaya. CPI bhi kafi badh hi gayi hai. Bhai itna bata raha hu tera UPSC bhi nikal jayaga. Aaram se aache se prepare karna. Mehnat mai kahi kami toh tu waise bhi rakhta nahi hai. 
All the Best.
author: Aryan  Choudhary

text:
4 saal mai tere saat reh kar bahut bakchodiya ki hai. Last time sab bhai log kisso ko yaad karne baithe the toh 1-1.5 ghanta toh zoom par aise hi nikal gaya tha. Baate katam nahi hui thi. Yaha sab likhne baitha toh waah tera poora page mai hi bhar dunga. Jis standup ke wajah se poore hall mai log tuje itna jante hai vo mere bachpane par hi based tha. Video toh uska aaj bhi pada hai mere paas. Uss din bhi tuje live perform karte hue toh nahi hi dekhta tha. Tua jo banna tha. ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚
Vo chipkali ko dekh kar tera jump karna.ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚
Sense of humor and satire toh mera bhi badiya hai. Tere saat rehte rehte hi seekha hu. Tuje toh IITK mai sirf bacche hi bol rahe hai ki tera satire badiya hai. Muje toh IITK mai ek prof ne kaha tha â€œAryan tu jokes aache marta haiâ€.

Tu meri alarm ko galiya deta hai ki jis din tera PE nahi tha uss din bhi mai tuje utha deti thi. Raat ko toh tu hi hum dono ko sone nahi deta tha. Tu pata kaha kaha se kisse utha kar lata tha. Bolna band hi nahi hota tha tera. Raat ke 12 baje ho ya 3/4/5.
Aur ha teri sim ka toh muje 2nd year ke end tak toh pata tha kaha padi hai. Aaj ka status pata nahi. 
First antaragni tera kisi ke saat CCD mai jane ka plan maine aache se barbad kiya tha maine. 

Mera first BDay toh tuje yaad hi hoga. Wing mai bhi logo ke maje lene ke mauke toh kabhi chode nahi hai. Govind toh aye din bade papa se complain karta tha. Uske saat jo prank kiya tha vo tohâ€¦ Truecaller par naam Aryan likha aa raha tha uske fir bhi aache se maje leh liye the uske.  â€œâ€Maine socha sis guard ka naam Aryan ho sakta hai.â€â€ ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ Uske maje bahut liye hai. Ek jana uski marta tha dushra usko sambalta tha.
 
Yeh corona katam ho toh kahi ghoomne chalte hai.
